headline: Carrum Health Doubles Covered Lives as Employers Confront Record Healthcare Costs
summary: Carrum Health, the leader in value-based Centers of Excellence (COE), today announced it has doubled its covered lives to 6.7M, adding 3.6M new lives in 2025 alone. The unprecedented growth reflects a fundamental market shift as employers face a perfect storm of healthcare costs.
